title: Coinbase Stock Hits New All-Time Low Amid Plummeting Yearly Revenues
dc:creator: Andrew Throuvalas
content: Coinbase’s stock (COIN) continues to slide as the exchange braces for year-end figures that grossly underperform its 2021 numbers.
